name: Rawamangun Junction (2015)
description:
Rawamangun is the first urban area in the current East Jakarta area that was built after Indonesia's independence. This junction is always busy because it connects the residential center to the North Jakarta area. In addition, traffic jams always occur because this junction is close to the sports center, bus terminal and Arion Mall. (2020)
